creator: Think Ladder Limited
descriptionHtml:
Thinkladder is a collaboration of mental health professionals, creatives, contributors, and developers that have teamed together to provide you with a beautiful self-discovery journey.

Thinkladder is a guide that helps link symptoms to underlying limiting beliefs and then offers the opportunity to challenge those beliefs with insights collated by our mental health professionals.

With Thinkladder, you can set reminders to help you build new thought patterns centred around the relevant insights that you have discovered.

Just like you, Thinkladder is growing. At the moment, you can explore themes including:

Social / Physical Distancing
Loss of Job
Perfectionism
Correction & Criticism
People Pleasing
I Must Be Dumb
Comparing Myself to Others
Self-Worth
Compassion Fatigue
Anxiety
Anger
Body Image
Startups and Founders

descriptionHtml:

• Understand why you feel and behave the way you do.
• Take daily steps toward feeling calmer, more resilient and self-aware.

Thinkladder is a mental wellbeing app that enables you to explore your belief system, weed out and replace limiting ideas that stop you from living your best life. Thinkladder pulls on simple CBT-based tools and methods, proven to improve your mental wellbeing. It only takes a few minutes each day to understand yourself better and move towards the change you want.

It only takes a few minutes each day to understand yourself better and move towards the change you want.

With Thinkladder, you can set reminders to help you build new thought patterns centred around the relevant Insights that you have discovered.
